<br>
Take Chardok for example, the &quot;Pairs&quot; configuration of mobs in the Zone in and Zone out are perfect for Charm soloing. Charm 1 mob, send it on the other. If they are the same level mobs, they will take each other down in HP equivalently. When both mobs are low on health, you <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>can</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Mez the mob, back off your pet, invis yourself (right click boot invis, why waste the mana on dispell?), and root your pet (who is now an NPC). When you do this, you still receive exp from nuking to death the two mobs.<br>
<br>
This to me is not an exploit. Using this method, I can probably get equivalent experience as each member of an average group of the same level. The reason that it wasn't <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>MORE</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> efficient than an entire group, was because the DPS and health of the charmed pets was not that significantly greater than the players I could have grouped with. However, as already mentioned, in PoP, the scenario has changed. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=60465">Xerphanis</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Arch Convoker</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kardazashgate>Kardaz Ashgate</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 47<br> <font color=#333333>(1/16/03 9:03:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=449.topic&index=25>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Charm solution? (Hopefully not redundant)</span><hr size=1> That is probably because mez has a memblur component... or things might have change. Mez also force the pet to back off which wipes the aggro from the pet too. I'll go check again when I get home. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kardazashgate>Kardaz Ashgate</A> at: 1/16/03 9:06:19 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=cantatus>Cantatus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 93<br> <font color=#333333>(1/16/03 9:25:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfr